			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>It depends on whether you were switching targets to mez and keep singing your songs whilst mezzing. If you do that I would say it is better to mez than let the warr tank 2 but if you are just keeping the mez run on the mezzed mob and just meleeing the warriors target there is an argument for letting the warr tank both as while the add is mezzed you are not hasting or slowing the mobs or providing a multitude of other things to the rest of the group which can help take down both mobs alot faster than if you were doing '1 at a time'</span></td>
